      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="全局配置"><a href="#全局配置" class="headerlink" title="全局配置"></a>全局配置</h1><p>在 _config.yml中可修改大部份的配置。<br><a id="more"></a><br>配置简要说明：(以我的网站为例)<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div><div class="line">74</div><div class="line">75</div><div class="line">76</div><div class="line">77</div><div class="line">78</div><div class="line">79</div><div class="line">80</div><div class="line">81</div><div class="line">82</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># Hexo Configuration</div><div class="line">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/configuration.html</div><div class="line">## Source: https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># Site       #下面是设置说明，注意 “：” 后面有空格</div><div class="line">title: time&apos;s notes    #网站标题</div><div class="line">subtitle: 囚笼         #网站副标题</div><div class="line">description: 未必明天，就有以后....  #网站签名</div><div class="line">author: sincethen      #用户</div><div class="line">email: sincethen@vip.qq.com #邮箱地址</div><div class="line">language: zh-Hans      #网站使用语言</div><div class="line">timezone:              #时区列表</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">avatar: /images/since.png  #作者头像存放位置，可为网页链接</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">search:                #站点内搜索</div><div class="line">  path: search.xml</div><div class="line">  field: post</div><div class="line">  </div><div class="line"># URL  #如果博客绑定域名 url要填写域名信息</div><div class="line">## If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as &apos;http://yoursite.com/child&apos; and root as &apos;/child/&apos;</div><div class="line">url: http://blog.kuxinhua.com</div><div class="line">root: /   #网站根目录</div><div class="line">permalink: :year/:month/:day/:title/  文章地址的链接格式</div><div class="line">permalink_defaults:</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># Directory   #目录</div><div class="line">source_dir: source   #资源文件夹，存放内容</div><div class="line">public_dir: public   #公共文件夹，存放生成站点文件</div><div class="line">tag_dir: tags        #标签文件夹</div><div class="line">archive_dir: archives #归档文件夹</div><div class="line">category_dir: categories #分类文件夹</div><div class="line">code_dir: downloads/code  #include code 文件夹</div><div class="line">i18n_dir: :lang      #国际化（i18n）文件夹</div><div class="line">skip_render:</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># Writing</div><div class="line">new_post_name: :title.md # 新文章名称</div><div class="line">default_layout: post     # 默认布局</div><div class="line">titlecase: false # Transform title into titlecase</div><div class="line">external_link: true # 在新标签页中打开链接</div><div class="line">filename_case: 0   #文件名称转换 (1)小写或(2)大写</div><div class="line">render_drafts: false</div><div class="line">post_asset_folder: false  #启动 Asset 文件夹</div><div class="line">relative_link: false      #把链接改为与根目录的相对位址，默认false</div><div class="line">future: true</div><div class="line">highlight:     #代码块的设置</div><div class="line">  enable: true</div><div class="line">  line_number: true</div><div class="line">  auto_detect: false</div><div class="line">  tab_replace:</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># Category &amp; Tag   #分类和标签的设置</div><div class="line">default_category: uncategorized   #默认分类</div><div class="line">category_map:</div><div class="line">tag_map:</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># Date / Time format  #时间格式</div><div class="line">## Hexo uses Moment.js to parse and display date</div><div class="line">## You can customize the date format as defined in</div><div class="line">## http://momentjs.com/docs/#/displaying/format/</div><div class="line">date_format: YYYY-MM-DD</div><div class="line">time_format: HH:mm:ss</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># Pagination   #首页显示的分页设置</div><div class="line">## Set per_page to 0 to disable pagination</div><div class="line">per_page: 10   #每页显示文章量</div><div class="line">pagination_dir: page  #分页目录</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># Extensions</div><div class="line">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</div><div class="line">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</div><div class="line">## theme: landscape</div><div class="line">theme: next     #当前主题名称</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">duoshuo_shortname: cpdl    #多说插件用户名称</div><div class="line"># Deployment</div><div class="line">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</div><div class="line">deploy:              #部署的设置</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repo: </div><div class="line">      github: git@github.com:cpdl/cpdl.github.io.git,master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="域名绑定"><a href="#域名绑定" class="headerlink" title="域名绑定"></a>域名绑定</h1><p>　　域名绑定分为两个步骤：</p>
<ul>
<li>在你域名注册解析的网站中，将域名指向仓库名<br><img src="http://ocubawuej.bkt.clouddn.com/yuming1.png" alt="域名解析"></li>
<li>网站目录中添加CNAME文件，指定网站域名 <blockquote>
<p>CNAME文件存放位置： 根目录下/source 文件夹中。假如网站目录 e:/hexo，那么存放位置是 e:/hexo/source/中<br>CNAME文件内容直接填写绑定域名信息。其它不用写。比如我的网站： blog.kuxinhua.com</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="添加主题"><a href="#添加主题" class="headerlink" title="添加主题"></a>添加主题</h1><ul>
<li><p>hexo 主题比较多。这里为大家介绍几个网站</p>
<ul>
<li>hexo-theme: <a href="https://hexo.io/themes/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></li>
<li>hexo-github-theme-list: <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/wiki/Themes" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/wiki/Themes</a></li>
<li>知乎上的讨论：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/24422335" target="_blank" rel="external">http://www.zhihu.com/question/24422335</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>我选择的是NEXT主题,比较干净纯洁。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="下载启用主题"><a href="#下载启用主题" class="headerlink" title="下载启用主题"></a>下载启用主题</h1><ul>
<li><p>使用git 克隆最新主题版本到 目录themes/ 中。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ cd e:/hexo</div><div class="line">$ git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>启用主题</p>
<ul>
<li>打开站点 <strong>配置文件</strong> ，修改theme字段值为：next<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">theme: next</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>验证主题</p>
<blockquote>
<p>启动本地Hexo站点，开启调试模式。命令是： hexo s –debug.<br>使用浏览器访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:4000</a> 检查站点是否正确运行。</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="主题设定"><a href="#主题设定" class="headerlink" title="主题设定"></a>主题设定</h1><h2 id="选择Scheme"><a href="#选择Scheme" class="headerlink" title="选择Scheme"></a>选择Scheme</h2><p>next主题提供三种Scheme外观。在主题配置文件中(/themes/next/_config/yml)切换。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">#scheme: Muse</div><div class="line">#scheme: Mist</div><div class="line">scheme: Pisces</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>Muse:默认的scheme，next最初版本，黑白主调，大量留白<br> Mist:Muse的紧凑版本，整洁有序的单栏外观<br> Pisces - 双栏Scheme，小家碧玉似的清新</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="主题语言"><a href="#主题语言" class="headerlink" title="主题语言"></a>主题语言</h2><ul>
<li><p>上节全局配置文件中说明中有设定。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>全局配置</strong>文件为：网站根目录下 _config.yml，不要和<strong>主题配置</strong>文件弄混淆。</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><p>一些常用语言如下：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>english: en<br>简体中文： zh-Hans<br>繁体中文： zh-hk或是 zh-tw</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="设置菜单"><a href="#设置菜单" class="headerlink" title="设置菜单"></a>设置菜单</h2><ul>
<li>菜单栏就是主页的导航栏。</li>
<li>菜单栏分为二个部分：第一菜单项（名称和链接），第二菜单项对应的图标和显示文本。</li>
<li><p>菜单项对应的配置是<strong>主题配置文件</strong>中的menu字段。设置格式是：item name: link.如下所示</p>
<ul>
<li>这其中 ：分类页，标签页，关于页和404页面要手动创建这个页面。<br><code>menu:
home: /        #next显示文本是：主页
categories: /categories    #分类页
#about: /about    #关于页面，前面加#表示不显示
#archives: /archives  #归档页
tags: /tags       #标签页
#search: /
#commonweal: /404.html    #404页面</code></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>手动创建页面</li>
<li>以归档页为例,网站根目录下执行git bash命令：<br><code>$ hexo new page &quot;archives&quot;
INFO  Created: E:\hexo\source\archives\index.md</code></li>
<li>编辑生成的页面：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">title: archives</div><div class="line">date: 2016-9-1 18:30:07</div><div class="line">type: &quot;archives&quot;    #添加类型为archives</div><div class="line">comments: false     #关闭评论</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>菜单项文字和图标</p>
<ul>
<li><p>菜单项显示的对应文字放置在网站使用主题目录下的 languages/{language}.yml （{language} 是网站使用的语言）。如下所示：<br><code>menu:
home: 首页
archives: 归档
categories: 分类
tags: 标签
about: 关于
search: 搜索
commonweal: 公益404</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>在NEXT主题中，显示的菜单图片是由<a href="http://fontawesome.io/icons/" target="_blank" rel="external">Font Awesome</a>提供的图片。</p>
</li>
<li>在<strong>主题配置文件</strong>中设置：配置方式为 <strong>菜单项: 菜单图片名</strong> 。<br><code>menu_icons:
enable: true   #启用图标
home: home     
about: user
categories: th
tags: tags
archives: archive
commonweal: heartbeat</code></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="设置侧栏位置"><a href="#设置侧栏位置" class="headerlink" title="设置侧栏位置"></a>设置侧栏位置</h2><ul>
<li>默认侧栏仅在文章页面（拥有目录列表）时才显示，并放置于右侧位置。</li>
<li><p>通过修改<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，可以控制侧栏的位置和显示的时机。</p>
</li>
<li><p>侧栏的位置参数值： </p>
<ul>
<li>left 靠左</li>
<li>right靠右</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>配置文件如下所示（/theme/next/_config.yml）：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">sidebar:</div><div class="line">　　position:left</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<ul>
<li>侧栏时机参数：<ul>
<li>post 　默认行为，在文章页面（拥有目录列表）显示 </li>
<li>always 在所有页面中都显示</li>
<li>hide　在所有页面中都隐藏（可以手动展开）</li>
<li>remove 完全移除<br>配置文件如下所示（/theme/next/_config.yml）:<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">sidebar:</div><div class="line">  display: post</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>##设置头像</p>
<ul>
<li><p>上面<strong>全局配置文件</strong>：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">avatar: /images/since.png</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>链接可为互联网URI,也或是站点内地址。注意此处站点内地址默认目录为source/下，比如/images/since.png,真实位置 source/images/since.png</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="设置作者名称"><a href="#设置作者名称" class="headerlink" title="设置作者名称"></a>设置作者名称</h2><ul>
<li><strong>全局配置文件</strong>：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">author: sincethen      #用户</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="设置-作者签名"><a href="#设置-作者签名" class="headerlink" title="设置 作者签名"></a>设置 作者签名</h2><ul>
<li><strong>全局配置文件</strong>：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">description: 未必明天，就有以后....  #网站签名</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="多说评论"><a href="#多说评论" class="headerlink" title="多说评论"></a>多说评论</h2><ul>
<li>注册多说帐号</li>
<li>创建站点，注意你创建的多说域名（<a href="http://xxx.duoshuo.com）xxx为将要添加的参数" target="_blank" rel="external">http://xxx.duoshuo.com）xxx为将要添加的参数</a>.</li>
<li>编辑<strong>站点配置文件</strong>，添加如下：<br><code>disqus_shortname:xxx</code></li>
<li>修改作者的评论显示的名称：<ul>
<li>获取用户ID：登陆多说，个人资料中，点击个人名字，在网址栏中<br><code>http://duoshuo.com/profile/xxxxxxxxxxxxxx/</code> ,最后一串数字。</li>
<li>在主题配置文件中(themes/next/_config.yml)，添加多说评论.如下所示：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">duoshuo_info:</div><div class="line">  ua_enable: true       #显示UA信息</div><div class="line">  admin_enable: ture</div><div class="line">  user_id: xxxxxxxxxx    #用户ID</div><div class="line">  admin_nickname: 作者大人</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="http://ocubawuej.bkt.clouddn.com/zhuti1.jpg" alt="评论结果"></p>
<h2 id="添加搜索"><a href="#添加搜索" class="headerlink" title="添加搜索"></a>添加搜索</h2><p>添加本地 站点内搜索：</p>
<ul>
<li><p>安装 hexo-generator-search，在站点的根目录下执行以下命令</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">cnpm install hexo-generator-search --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>编辑<strong>站点配置文件</strong>，新增以下内容（可参看最上面的配置）：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">search:</div><div class="line">  path: search.xml</div><div class="line">  field: post</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
